                <h1>Discover the Legacy of Christian Dior: Fashion Icon</h1>
                <p>Christian Dior, a French fashion designer, revolutionized women's fashion in the mid-20th century with his iconic “New Look,” characterized by cinched waists and full skirts. Born in 1905, Dior founded his luxury fashion house in 1946, offering elegance and sophistication. His legacy lives on through timeless designs and a renowned brand.</p>
